00:08:31.989 --> 00:08:32.989
I found that last night.

00:08:32.989 --> 00:08:34.085
STUDENT: Oh, neat!

00:08:34.085 --> 00:08:35.460
PROFESSOR: I don't
know exactly--

00:08:35.460 --> 00:08:37.090
STUDENT: And then chirp
is it's periodically

00:08:37.090 --> 00:08:38.219
